article_title: U.S. Rep. Dave Reichert, seeking a sixth term, faces challenge from ‘yellow dog Democrat’
article_text: Incumbent Republican Congressman Dave Reichert holds most of the advantages in his quest for a sixth term. Newcomer Jason Ritchie, a self-described from a midwestern union family, hopes to unseat him.
